article.headline: Conwell's 16 lead Xavier over Siena 80-55
article.description: — Ryan Conwell scored 16 points as Xavier beat Siena 80-55 on Wednesday night.
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Ryan Conwell scored 16 points as Xavier beat Siena 80-55 on Wednesday night. Conwell shot 6 for 9, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Musketeers (5-0). Trey Green shot 5 for 8, including 4 for 7 from beyond the arc to add 14 points. Marcus Foster had 12 points and finished 5 of 7 from the field. The Saints (3-2) were led by Reid Ducharme, who recorded 15 points. Major Freeman added 12 points for Siena. Green led Xavier in scoring with nine points in the first half to help go ahead 44-28 at the break. Xavier pulled away with an 8-0 run in the second half to extend an 18-point lead to 26 points. Conwell led the way with a team-high 10 second-half points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
